text: Dean Martin worked as the Arizona State Treasurer - the leader banker - for a time of four years, starting in 2007 and ending in 2011. He was a person who belonged to a group called the Republican Party. This person won against another person from a group called the Democratic Party, named Rano Singh, in an important event called the 2006 general election. Before, Martin used to be a part of the Arizona Senate.Arizona State Treasurer Dean Martin == References == Category:Politicians from Phoenix, Arizona Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
title: Dean Martin (politician)
